        <num>CCRP 712</num>
        <heading>712.  Discretionary grounds</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 712.  Discretionary grounds
A motion for continuance, if timely filed, may be granted, in the discretion of the court, in any case if there is good ground therefor.</p>
        </content>
